{
  "stem": "1799.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were three groups-- the young, the middle, and the older ones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The young were age group of 5 to 8.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The middle ones were a 9 to 12.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then the older ones were the teens, and to 15.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that was part of my group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had a school in that home, which was run by ORT, O-R-T.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it consisted of leather work, [NON-ENGLISH], leather work which was taught by a Russian-born Jew who had lived in France quite a while.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was supposed to be what we could do as, as trade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "ORT, even today, believed in helping young Jewish people to acquire a trade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was done there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we also had a, like, a boarding school going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had three or four different teachers where we learned various, like, math and French and literature, and some other subjects, which was not attended by everyone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was attended by those who were able to follow those courses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Some of those students, I'm proud to say, we are in touch with today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The group that formed at that time, like a family, over the two years that I was there, became a very closely-knit group as we shared studies and the learning of the leather trade, and the general being together.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there from-- yes, just about two years, a little longer, two years and two months.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not aware of any interference from anywhere, or any pogrom, or any hassle from antisemitic activities whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that moment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was aware.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I went to visit my father, who then lived in Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were aware.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the war, as it was settled in Europe-- let me try and think.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
